WEBVTT

00:05:57.698 --> 00:06:00.282
"campaign finance reform."

00:06:00.282 --> 00:06:03.010
Eighteen months later,

00:06:03.010 --> 00:06:04.820
at the age of 90,

00:06:04.820 --> 00:06:07.346
she arrived in Washington
with hundreds following her,

00:06:07.346 --> 00:06:09.664
including many congressmen
who had gotten in a car

00:06:09.664 --> 00:06:12.572
and driven out about a mile outside of the city

00:06:12.572 --> 00:06:14.460
to walk in with her.

00:06:14.460 --> 00:06:16.602
(Laughter)

00:06:16.602 --> 00:06:19.892
Now, I don't have 13 months

00:06:19.892 --> 00:06:21.534
to walk across the country.

00:06:21.534 --> 00:06:24.176
I've got three kids who hate to walk,

00:06:24.176 --> 00:06:25.578
and a wife who, it turns out,

00:06:25.578 --> 00:06:27.476
still hates when I'm not there

00:06:27.476 --> 00:06:28.645
for mysterious reasons,

00:06:28.645 --> 00:06:29.950
so this was not an option,

00:06:29.950 --> 00:06:31.110
but the question I asked,